{"name": "number-names", "metadata": {"name": "number_names", "version": "0.1.1", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU General Public License v3 or later (GPLv3+)", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "This module provides functions for getting the English names of numbers.", "upload_time": 1734558852}, "documentation": ["# Number Names\n\n`number_names` converts numbers to their English names.\n\nThe main useful function this package provides is called `name`. Usage\nis as follows:\n\n```python\n>>> import number_names\n>>> number_names.name(0)\n'zero'\n>>> number_names.name(1)\n'one'\n>>> number_names.name(2)\n'two'\n>>> number_names.name(123_456_789)\n'one hundred and twenty three million four hundred and fifty six thousand seven hundred and eighty nine'\n>>> number_names.name(3.1415)\n'three point one four one five'\n>>> number_names.name(-10 ** 15)\n'minus one quadrillion'\n>>> number_names.name(10 ** 100000)\n'ten tretriginmilliatrecenduotrigintillion'\n>>> number_names.name(3 + 2j)\n'three plus two i'\n>>> from fractions import Fraction\n>>> number_names.name(Fraction(1, 2))\n'one half'\n>>> number_names.name(Fraction(3, 221))\n'three two hundred and twenty firsts'\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "number_names", "documentation": ["This module provides functions for getting the English names of numbers."], "functions": [{"name": "number_names._words", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "function", "type": {"name": "Callable", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Callable", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "...", "xref": null, "params": null}, {"name": "Iterable", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Iterable", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}]}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Callable", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Callable", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "...", "xref": null, "params": null}, {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "number_names._power_name", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "power_index", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "number_names._to_thousand_name", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "number", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Iterator", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Iterator", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "number_names._denominator_name", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "number_names.integer_name", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "number", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Iterator", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Iterator", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": ["Get the English name of an integer."]}, {"name": "number_names.decimal_name", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "number", "type": {"name": "Decimal", "xref": {"fqname": "decimal.Decimal", "project": "--std--"}, "pa